{
  "texts": [
    "Improvements are especially significant from 25 to 50% comfort weight, and decrease as the comfort weight increases (although always improving).",
    "Page 23 of 39 173",
    "However, there are two exceptions where assigning 100% weight to comfort means some worsening from 75%.",
    "This is the case for SAC in hot climate and TD3 in cool climate.",
    "In Sect. 6.4 we will discuss possible causes for these exceptions."
  ]
}